title: USA Championships Day 2
description: O'Neill Groms continue to advance at the USA Championships with Jake Davis, Colt Ward, Kain Daly and Kei Kobayashi all advancing. O'Neill Girls contender Kiana Forres from Kauai had a shocker of a heat when in the final seconds of her heat her opponent got a late scoring wave to edge Kiana into 3rd.
